title: Legends of Solitaire 2 [FINAL] 2013 (PC) Foxy Games
description:
Game Description:
******************
It was market day, and the villagers bustled about their daily business, tending their animals and peddling their wares while the Kings Guard kept watch from the castle atop the hill. It was safe here, for the time being, but rumors of the approaching evil could be heard whispered in the tavern. There was time to rest and gather supplies for the adventure ahead, but not much. All across the land, villages like this were burning, and castles just as mighty had fallen. The kingdom was in need of a champion!. Might ye be the champion to save them?
